Business or Commercial Purposes for Which Information is Collected
We may use your personal information for any of the following purposes:
Providing our services to you and allowing you to participate in the features the ALDI Services offer;
Recognizing you across devices so as to improve your experience with us;
Identifying your preferences and tailor our content and recommendations for you;
Processing your transactions;
Process your registration when you sign up for an account
Manage and execute delivery and grocery pick-up services;
Providing information on products/services we think you may be interested in;
Responding to your requests for information;
Verifying your identity, including without limitation, for purposes of product reviews;
Provide interest-based content and advertising to you based on the way you browse or shop on the Services and other platforms;
Improving our services and marketing endeavors;
Communicate with you about your requests, questions and comments, and administer your participation in special events, programs, surveys, contests, sweepstakes, and other offers or promotions from us and third party marketing offers from our trusted partners, as well as from other companies;
Contact you about your use of the Services or similar administrative communications, or to provide you with Service updates, newsletters and other informational materials;
Operate, evaluate and improve our Services and business (including developing new products and services; determining the effectiveness of our sales, marketing and advertising; and analyzing and enhancing our products, services and Services, including our mobile applications);
For internal business purposes;
Complying with the law and protecting the safety, rights, property, or security of ALDI, the ALDI Services, consumers, and the general public;
Investigating and preventing fraud, illegal activities, and activities that violate our policies, and resolving technical issues reported about the ALDI Services;
Other purposes disclosed to you at the time you provide your information, or otherwise with your consent.
