Global Privacy Control
Global Privacy Control (“GPC”) is a technical specification in your browser settings that you can use to automatically inform websites of your privacy preferences with regard to third party online tracking.  To find out more about and set up GPC, please visit
https://globalprivacycontrol.org/#about
. We listen for and honor GPC signals as required under the applicable laws.
