Changing Your Information
You are responsible for maintaining the accuracy of the information you submit to us, such as your contact information provided as part of registration. Certain Services allow you to correct or update certain personal information you have provided. Note that when you edit your personal information or change your preferences on a Service, information that you remove may persist internally for our administrative purposes or within backup media. If you have made any public postings on a Service, these communications cannot generally be removed.
