How We Protect Personal Information
We maintain commercially reasonable and appropriate administrative, technical and physical safeguards designed to maintain the personal information we collect in a secure manner.  Even though we follow reasonable procedures to try to protect the information in our possession, no data transmission over the Internet, wireless transmission or electronic storage of information can be guaranteed to be 100% secure. ALDI cannot ensure or warrant the security of any information we collect. You use the Services and provide us information at your own risk.
