Notice to Nevada Residents
N.R.S. 603A provides consumers with the ability to opt out of the sale of their personal information. If you are a Nevada resident, you may submit an opt-out request by sending an email to
data.privacy@aldi.us
. Your request must include your full name, street address, city, state, zip code, and a valid email address so that we can contact you if needed regarding your request. If you previously provided a phone number, including it will assist us in making sure we identify you as someone who wants to opt out. You may be required to take reasonable steps as we determine from time to time to verify your identity and/or the authenticity of your request.
